Cannot start TaskFlow dev because these ports are already in use: frontend dev port localhost:3121.
Close the process using those ports or override them for this session.
Quick localhost fallback: pnpm dev:localhost --turbo
PowerShell example: $env:FRONTEND_PORT=3121; $env:BACKEND_PORT=5121; pnpm dev --turbo
Bash example: FRONTEND_PORT=3121 BACKEND_PORT=5121 pnpm dev --turbo
